    "cultural_notes": "Fried macaroni is a staple of modern Ugandan home cooking, especially in urban areas. It's a go-to recipe for a fast, affordable, and filling meal that everyone in the family enjoys. It reflects the adaptability of Ugandan cuisine, incorporating pasta into everyday cooking with a local flavor profile using common vegetables and spices."
